TextEng: What could you possibly have to talk about?
Text: 도대체 무슨 얘기를 할 게 있다는 거지?

TextEng: Never! Evil creatures like yourself must die!
Text: 절대 안 돼! 너 같은 악한 놈들은 죽어야 해!

TextEng: Why? I love killing goblins!
Text: 왜? 나는 고블린 죽이는 걸 좋아하는데!

TextEng: Is there anything more about the master that you know?
Text: 주인에 대해 더 아는 게 있나?

TextEng: Sounds like the other chiefs would pay for *your* head.
Text: 다른 족장들이 네 머리에 현상금을 걸 것 같은데.

TextEng: No, I'd rather kill you.
Sounds like you have yourself a deal, goblin.
What about the army you mentioned?
Text: 네가 말한 군대에 대해 더 말해봐.

TextEng: But what *is* this Dergiab?
I have the head of the bugbear chieftain.
I have the head of the orc chieftain.
Time for you to die, goblin!
Nothing. I'll be on my way.
Well, now it's time to kill you, I'm afraid!
I'll leave you to your joy, then.
Talk? Hah! You not know how talk gooder.
Text: 말? 하! 너 말도 제대로 못 해.

TextEng: Me think all evil creatures same: dead!
Text: 나 생각엔 악한 놈들 다 똑같아: 죽어야 해!

TextEng: But me loves killing goblins. Lots of good fun!
Text: 나 고블린 죽이는 거 좋아해. 엄청 재밌어!

TextEng: What you tells me more of master?
Me think other chieftains pay for your head!
Text: 나 생각엔 다른 족장들이 너 머리에 돈 줄 거야!

TextEng: No. Me likes killing you instead.
Text: 아니. 나 너 죽이는 게 좋아.

TextEng: Me accepts deal. Me do this.
Me gots bugbear chieftain head!
Me wents and chopped orc chieftain's head!
Text: 나 가서 오크 족장 머리 잘랐어!

TextEng: Me kills goblin now!
Me not want nothing. Me leave.
Text: 나 아무것도 안 원해. 나 가.

TextEng: What you tells me more of army.
Is Dergiab monster? What it be?
Me kill all else. Now me kill you, too.
Text: 나 다른 놈들 다 죽였어. 이제 너도 죽여.

TextEng: Okay. Stay happy. Bye.
I have a question.
Me can ask you question, yes?
What can you tell me about the master?
Text: 주인에 대해 뭘 알려줄 수 있어?

TextEng: What you tells me of master?
What about the army you mentioned?
Text: 네가 말한 군대에 대해 더 말해봐.

TextEng: What you tells me more of army.
